---
import BaseLayout from '@/components/layout/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Moe Qadan — Product Designer & UX Engineer"
  description="Designing and shipping product end to end. Currently: ChatOBD2 (AI-native diagnostics) and the MagTek platform. Previously: advisor tools at Chase, Cetera, Northwestern Mutual via InvestCloud."
  keywords={[
    'Moe Qadan',
    'about',
    'product designer',
    'UX engineer',
    'design engineer',
    'background',
    'experience',
    'AI-native systems',
  ]}
>
  <div class="about">
    <div class="about__hero">
      <div class="container-site">
        <span class="about__eyebrow">About</span>
        <h1 class="about__title">
          Moe Qadan, <em>plain</em>.
        </h1>
        <p class="about__hero-sub">
          Product designer and UX engineer. Currently shipping product
          across long-running platforms and AI-native systems, where the
          model is one stage in a structured pipeline.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container-site about__body">
      <div class="about__prose">
        <p class="about__lead">
          Most of my work isn't about building from scratch. It's about
          stepping into what already exists and making it better.
        </p>

        <p class="about__para">
          Understand the constraints. Improve the structure instead of
          adding complexity. Build patterns that get reused, not just
          shipped. Know when to automate and when not to.
        </p>

        <p class="about__signature">
          Most systems don't need to be replaced. They need to be
          understood first.
        </p>

        <hr class="about__rule" />

        <h2 class="about__h2">Background</h2>

        <ol class="about__career">
          <li class="about__career-item about__career-item--current">
            <header class="about__career-head">
              <span class="about__career-status">Current</span>
              <h3 class="about__career-title">ChatOBD2</h3>
              <span class="about__career-period">2025 — present</span>
            </header>
            <p class="about__career-desc">
              Founder &amp; sole designer / engineer. AI-native automotive
              diagnostics product I designed, engineered, and shipped end
              to end. Mobile app, marketing site, developer portal,
              backend pipeline.
            </p>
            <p class="about__career-stack">
              React Native (Expo), TypeScript, Supabase, BLE, structured
              prompt pipeline.
            </p>
          </li>

          <li class="about__career-item about__career-item--current">
            <header class="about__career-head">
              <span class="about__career-status">Current</span>
              <h3 class="about__career-title">MagTek</h3>
              <span class="about__career-period">Now</span>
            </header>
            <p class="about__career-desc">
              UX systems and frontend architecture across MagTek.com and
              a network of related sites on a shared, long-running
              ASP.NET MVC platform. Razor component library, design
              tokens, layout primitives, navigation grammar.
            </p>
            <p class="about__career-stack">
              ASP.NET MVC, C#, Razor, Bootstrap, hand-authored CSS,
              JavaScript.
            </p>
          </li>

          <li class="about__career-item">
            <header class="about__career-head">
              <span class="about__career-status">Past</span>
              <h3 class="about__career-title">InvestCloud</h3>
              <span class="about__career-period">Earlier</span>
            </header>
            <p class="about__career-desc">
              Advisor- and customer-facing portals deployed across major
              wealth and banking institutions including Chase, Cetera,
              Northwestern Mutual, Voya, Silicon Valley Bank, and East
              West Bank. Multi-tenant frontend, per-institution branding,
              dense data layouts.
            </p>
            <p class="about__career-stack">
              CSS, proprietary CMS / component framework, Figma handoff
              translation.
            </p>
          </li>
        </ol>

        <hr class="about__rule" />

        <h2 class="about__h2">A few things that shape the work</h2>

        <ol class="about__list">
          <li>
            <strong>Systems before surfaces.</strong> A page is a render
            of something deeper. Get the underlying structure right and
            the surface gets cheaper to change.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Constraints are the brief.</strong> A long-running
            platform, a legacy stack, a business that depends on what's
            already running. Those aren't obstacles. They're the actual
            design problem.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>AI is infrastructure, not a feature.</strong>
            Prompts live in the system, scoped to context, versioned,
            and budgeted. The point is repeatability, not novelty.
          </li>
        </ol>

        <p class="about__para about__para--note">
          More on the workflow — Claude, Cursor, Figma, and how visual
          exploration fits in — lives on the
          <a href="/approach" class="about__inline-link">Approach</a> page.
        </p>

        <hr class="about__rule" />

        <h2 class="about__h2">The kind of work I take on</h2>

        <ul class="about__interests">
          <li>Long-running platforms with real constraints</li>
          <li>AI-native products where structure beats vibes</li>
          <li>System-level UX, not single-page polish</li>
          <li>Frontend architecture in environments that can't be torn down</li>
          <li>Tooling and workflows where AI is the delivery layer, not the demo</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <aside class="about__aside">
        <div class="about__card">
          <h3 class="about__card-title">Currently</h3>
          <ul class="about__card-list">
            <li>
              <span class="about__card-key">Status</span>
              <span class="about__card-val about__card-val--status">
                <span class="about__card-status-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                Open to projects
              </span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="about__card-key">Best fit</span>
              <span class="about__card-val">Product systems · UX engineering · AI-native products</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="about__card-key">Building</span>
              <span class="about__card-val">ChatOBD2 · MagTek platform</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="about__card-key">Stack</span>
              <span class="about__card-val">TypeScript · React · Astro · ASP.NET MVC · C# · Razor</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="about__card">
          <h3 class="about__card-title">Reach out</h3>
          <p class="about__card-note">
            Tell me what you're building. Replies usually within a day.
          </p>
          <a href="/contact" class="about__card-cta">
            Get in touch
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about__hero {
    padding-top: calc(60px + var(--space-10));
    padding-bottom: var(--space-10);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .about__hero {
      padding-top: calc(64px + var(--space-16));
      padding-bottom: var(--space-12);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
    }
  }

  .about__eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text-subtle);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .about__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(40px, 9.5vw, 80px);
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    line-height: 1.05;
    color: var(--color-text);
    max-width: 18ch;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }

  .about__title em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .about__hero-sub {
    font-size: clamp(16px, 1.7vw, 19px);
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  .about__body {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-10);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .about__body {
      gap: var(--space-12);
      padding-bottom: var(--space-24);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .about__body {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px;
      gap: var(--space-16);
    }
  }

  .about__lead {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(22px, 2.4vw, 28px);
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
    max-width: 56ch;
    font-weight: 400;
    padding-left: var(--space-5);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--color-accent);
  }

  .about__para {
    font-size: clamp(15px, 1.5vw, 17px);
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  .about__para--note {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-text-subtle);
    line-height: 1.65;
    padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-4);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background-color: var(--color-bg-muted);
    max-width: 60ch;
    margin-top: var(--space-2);
  }

  .about__inline-link {
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: var(--color-border);
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    transition: color 150ms, text-decoration-color 150ms;
  }

  .about__inline-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration-color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .about__signature {
    margin-top: var(--space-8);
    padding: var(--space-5) var(--space-6);
    background-color: var(--color-bg-muted);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(17px, 1.9vw, 21px);
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--color-text);
    max-width: 56ch;
  }

  .about__rule {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    margin: var(--space-12) 0 var(--space-10);
  }

  .about__h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(24px, 2.8vw, 34px);
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  /* Career timeline — adds the proof of seniority that was missing */
  .about__career {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  .about__career-item {
    padding: var(--space-5);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    background-color: var(--color-bg-elevated);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  @media (min-width: 600px) {
    .about__career-item {
      padding: var(--space-6) var(--space-7);
    }
  }

  .about__career-item--current {
    border-color: var(--color-accent-muted);
    background-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 80% at 100% 0%, var(--color-accent-dim), transparent 65%);
  }

  .about__career-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .about__career-status {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text-subtle);
    padding: 3px 8px;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    background-color: var(--color-bg-muted);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .about__career-item--current .about__career-status {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    background-color: var(--color-accent-dim);
    border-color: var(--color-accent-muted);
  }

  .about__career-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(22px, 2.4vw, 28px);
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin: 0;
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .about__career-period {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-text-subtle);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .about__career-desc {
    font-size: clamp(14px, 1.4vw, 16px);
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  .about__career-stack {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--color-text-subtle);
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin: 0;
    padding-top: var(--space-3);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
  }

  .about__list {
    counter-reset: about-list;
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .about__list li {
    counter-increment: about-list;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 36px;
    font-size: clamp(15px, 1.5vw, 17px);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  .about__list li::before {
    content: counter(about-list, decimal-leading-zero);
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 4px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .about__list strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .about__interests {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  .about__interests li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 24px;
    font-size: clamp(15px, 1.5vw, 17px);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text);
    padding-block: var(--space-2);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
  }

  .about__interests li::before {
    content: '+';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .about__interests li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  /* Sidebar */
  .about__aside {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .about__card {
    padding: var(--space-5);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    background-color: var(--color-bg-elevated);
  }

  .about__card-title {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text-subtle);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .about__card-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .about__card-list li {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .about__card-key {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-text-subtle);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .about__card-val {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.45;
  }

  .about__card-val--status {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 7px;
    color: var(--color-success);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .about__card-status-dot {
    width: 7px;
    height: 7px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: var(--color-success);
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-success) 65%, transparent);
    animation: about-status-pulse 2.4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes about-status-pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
    50% { opacity: 0.7; transform: scale(0.85); }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .about__card-status-dot { animation: none; }
  }

  .about__card-note {
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .about__card-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding-bottom: 4px;
    transition: color 150ms, border-color 150ms;
  }

  .about__card-cta:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    border-bottom-color: var(--color-accent);
  }
</style>
